T_ConfigItem_CatheterTypePressureLimitSe.Source: Default is recommended except in cases where maintaining flow rate or limiting pressure is critical. Changing the pressure limit sensitivity to "Low" allows the system more flexibility to maintain the desired flow rate, while a "High" sensitivity ensures the system reduces flow to prevent pressure from exceeding the programmed limit.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Aut.Source: After an exam ends and a new Patient Line is connected, controls if this reservoir will automatically be emptied.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Aut.Source: The system will automatically empty the Day Set when a new Patient Line is inserted at the end of an exam.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Cha.Source: Allows the contrast loaded in the Day Set to be changed to a different, compatible one.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Cou.Source: System behaviors may differ based on the installed country. Restart required.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Def.Source: When the extended length line is available and Preload Protocol is being used, this is the length that is selected by default.
T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Def.Translation: Når den forlængede linjelængde er tilgængelig, og Præpåfyld protokol bruges, er dette den længde, der er valgt som standard.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Ext.Source: The extended length Patient Line is not available in all markets and may not be available for use with this injector.  If it is available enable this to allow Preload Protocol to work with it.
T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Ext.Translation: Patientslangen med forlænget længde er ikke tilgængelig på alle markeder og er muligvis ikke tilgængelig til brug med denne injektor.  Hvis den er tilgængelig, skal du aktivere den for at tillade Præpåfyld protokol at arbejde med den.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Max.Source: The system, when reducing flow to limit the pressure from exceeding the programmed pressure limit, will reduce the flow rate by a maximum of this configured value. E.g. 40% means that a programmed flow rate of 5mL/s will be reduced to no lower than 3mL/s.
T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Max.Translation: Når systemet reducerer strømningen for at forhindre trykket i at overskride den programmerede trykgrænse, reducerer systemet strømningshastigheden med maksimalt denne konfigurerede værdi. Fx betyder 40 %, at en programmeret strømningshastighed på 5 ml/s højst reduceres til 3 ml/s.
Standard for maksimal reduktion af strømningshastighed

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Pre.Source: High sensitivity ensures that all efforts will be taken to prevent the pressure from reaching the pressure limit, while Low sensitivity will give the system greater flexibility to maintain the programmed flow rate while still limiting pressure from greatly exceeding the pressure limit.
T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Behaviors_Pre.Translation: Høj følsomhed sikrer, at alle anstrengelser gøres for at forhindre, at trykket når trykgrænsen, mens lav følsomhed vil give systemet større fleksibilitet til at opretholde den programmerede strømningshastighed, mens det stadig forhindrer trykket i at overskride trykgrænsen.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Exam_DisableW.Source: If CENT-MWL is licensed, Hide the Patient screen and associated worklist functionality. Restart required.
T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Exam_DisableW.Translation: Hvis CENT-MWL er licenseret, skjules patientskærmen og tilhørende arbejdslistefunktionalitet. Genstart påkrævet.

T_ConfigItem_Configuration_Exam_ExamTime.Source: The system will automatically end an exam after the configured amount of hours of inactivity.  Set to 0 to disable.

T_CRUFactoryDefaultAborted_UserDirection.Source:
WinRE 'Troubleshoot, Centargo Factory Default' either was not selected or had an error.

Try again and if this problem persists factory default cannot be done and a full manual re-installation is required.
T_CRUFactoryDefaultAborted_UserDirection.Translation:
WinRE ”Fejlfinding, Centargo-fabriksindstilling” var enten ikke valgt eller var fejlbehæftet.

Prøv igen, og hvis problemet fortsætter, kan fabriksindstillingerne ikke udføres, og det er nødvendigt med en fuldstændig manuel geninstallation.

T_CRUFactoryDefaultInstructions_UserDire.Source: On restart into WinRE choose 'Troubleshoot, Centargo Factory Default'.
T_CRUFactoryDefaultInstructions_UserDire.Translation: Ved genstart i WinRE skal du vælge "Fejlfinding, Centargo-fabriksindstilling".

T_CRUFactoryDefaultRemoteNotSupported_Na.Source: CRU Factory Default, No Remote Support

T_CRUFactoryDefaultRemoteNotSupported_Us.Source:
CRU Factory Default operations cannot be performed remotely.

VirtualCare remote support cannot be used.
T_CRUFactoryDefaultRemoteNotSupported_Us.Translation:
CRU-fabriksindstillingshandlinger kan ikke foretages eksternt.

VirtualCares fjernsupport kan ikke anvendes.

T_CRUFactoryDefaultRestoreInProgress_Use.Source:
Factory Default in progress.

CRU will reboot when finished.

Do not power off.
T_CRUFactoryDefaultRestoreInProgress_Use.Translation:
Fabriksindstilling i gang.

CRU genstarter, når den er færdig.

Sluk ikke for strømmen.

T_CruLostCommAbandonExam_Message.Source:
An exam is in progress, but there is no connection to the injector. If the exam is continued at the injector while there is no connection, those injections will not be recorded.

Either 'Wait' for the connection to be restored and finish the exam normally, or 'Abandon' the exam to record the current progress.
T_CruLostCommAbandonExam_Message.Translation:
En undersøgelse er i gang, men der er ingen forbindelse til injektoren. Hvis undersøgelsen fortsætter med injektoren, uden der er forbindelse, vil injektionerne ikke blive registreret.

Vælg enten ”Vent”, indtil forbindelsen er genoprettet, og afslut undersøgelsen normalt eller ”Forlad” undersøgelsen for at registrere det aktuelle fremskridt.

T_CruLostCommWhileInjecting_Message.Source:
Injection will complete normally.

Go to scan room to operate injector.
T_CruLostCommWhileInjecting_Message.Translation:
Injektion vil fuldføre normalt.

Gå til scanningsrummet for at anvende injektoren.

You may try again but a TAC Report should be taken and returned for investigation.

Der opstod en fejl under sikkerhedskopiering af data forud for opgradering.

Du kan forsøge igen, men der skal udarbejdes en TAC-rapport, som skal sendes tilbage til undersøgelse.

T_CRUUpgradeAbortedInPhase2_UserDirectio.Source:
WinRE 'Troubleshoot, Centargo Upgrade' either was not selected or had an error.

Try again and if this problem persists automatic upgrades cannot be done and a full manual installation is required.
T_CRUUpgradeAbortedInPhase2_UserDirectio.Translation:
WinRE ”Fejlfinding, Centargo-opgradering” var enten ikke valgt eller var fejlbehæftet.

Prøv igen, og hvis problemet fortsætter, kan automatiske opgraderinger ikke udføres, og det er nødvendigt med en fuldstændig manuel geninstallation.

T_CRUUpgradeAbortedInPhase3_UserDirectio.Source:
An exception occurred while restoring data after upgrading.

This unit no longer has the customer's data present and it must be manually restored.

A TAC Report should be taken and returned for investigation.
T_CRUUpgradeAbortedInPhase3_UserDirectio.Translation:
Der opstod en undtagelse under gendannelse af data efter opgradering.

Denne enhed indeholder ikke længere kundens data, og den skal gendannes manuelt.

Der skal udarbejdes en TAC-rapport, som skal sendes tilbage til undersøgelse.

T_CRUUpgradeCompleted_UserDirection.Source:
Data was backed-up, software was upgraded, and the backup was restored.

Ensure that the SRU is running a compatible version.
T_CRUUpgradeCompleted_UserDirection.Translation:
Der blev taget sikkerhedskopi af data, software blev opgraderet, og sikkerhedskopien blev gendannet.

Sørg for, at SRU'en kører en kompatibel version.

CRU genstarter automatisk, når gendannelsen er afsluttet.

Do not power off.

T_CRUUpgradeInProgress_UserDirection.Translation:
CRU genstarter flere gange.

T_IodineWizard_Q1_WhatConc_Guidance.Source:
If more than one concentration is used with this protocol, convert this protocol twice -- once for each.

(If the contrast media that you use is not listed, please finish setting up the injector under Admin/Contrasts.)
T_IodineWizard_Q1_WhatConc_Guidance.Translation:
Hvis der anvendes mere end én koncentration med denne protokol, skal denne protokol konverteres to gange – én gang for hver.

(Hvis det anvendte kontrastmedie ikke er angivet, skal du afslutte opsætningen af injektoren under Admin/Kontraster.)

T_IodineWizard_Q1_WhatConc_ImplicationWh.Translation: For denne protokol der bruger denne koncentration er jodindholdet {0}, og jodindgiftshastigheden er {1}.

T_IodineWizard_Q1_WhatConc_Question.Source: What contrast media concentration is typically used with this protocol?

T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_Guidance.Source: If the technologist is supposed to change this protocol's volumes or flow rates based on a patient's size, then answer Yes.
T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_Guidance.Translation: Hvis teknikeren skal ændre denne protokols volumener eller flowhastigheder baseret på patientens størrelse, skal du svare Ja.

T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_ImplicationW.Source: The amount of iodine given to a patient will not vary with their size.
T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_ImplicationW.Translation: Mængden af jod, der gives til en patient, varierer ikke i forhold til vedkommendes størrelse.

T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_ImplicationW.Source: The amount of iodine will vary with patient size (smaller will get less and larger will get more), and the technologist will need to enter it.
T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_ImplicationW.Translation: Mængden af jod varierer afhængigt af patientens størrelse (mindre vil få mindre, og større vil få mere), og teknikeren skal indtaste den.

T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_Question.Source: Should this protocol be adjusted for patients of different sizes?
T_IodineWizard_Q2_SizeAdapt_Question.Translation: Skal denne protokol justeres for patienter med forskellige størrelser?

T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_Guidance.Source:
Patient weight is most common, but it is also possible to use Lean Body Weight (LBW) or Body Surface Area (BSA).

LBW and BSA would have to be estimated using a published formula, and the technologist would have to enter it.
T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_Guidance.Translation:
Patientvægt er mest almindelig, men det er også muligt at bruge LBW (Lean Body Weight - Fedtfri vægt) eller BSA (Body Surface Area- Kropsoverfladeareal).

LBW og BSA skal estimeres ved hjælp af en offentliggjort formel, og teknikeren skal indtaste den.

T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Source: The technologist will have to calculate and enter the patient's estimated BSA.
T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Translation: Teknikeren skal beregne og indtaste patientens estimerede BSA.
T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.ExampleContext: BSA stands for Body Surface Area

T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Source: The technologist will have to calculate and enter the patient's estimated LBW.
T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Translation: Teknikeren skal beregne og indtaste patientens estimerede LBW.

T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Source: The technologist will have to either enter the patient's weight or confirm the value from the modality worklist (if available).
T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_ImplicationWh.Translation: Teknikeren skal enten indtaste patientens vægt eller bekræfte værdien fra modalitetsarbejdslisten (hvis tilgængelig).

T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_Question.Source: Do you want to adjust this protocol based on the patient's weight, lean body weight (LBW) or Body surface Area (BSA)?
T_IodineWizard_Q21_AdaptOn_Question.Translation: Vil du justere denne protokol baseret på patientens vægt eller fedtfri vægt (LBW) eller kropsoverfladeareal (BSA)?

T_IodineWizard_Q3_IsForCTA_Guidance.Source: If this protocol is primarily used for first-pass imaging, then it likely is for angiography.
T_IodineWizard_Q3_IsForCTA_Guidance.Translation: Hvis denne protokol primært bruges til first-pass billeddannelse, er det sandsynligvis til angiografi.

T_IodineWizard_Q3_IsForCTA_ImplicationWh.Source: For organ imaging, the total iodine load is the key variable.
T_IodineWizard_Q3_IsForCTA_ImplicationWh.Translation: Ved organbilleddannelse er den samlede jodmængde den afgørende variabel.

T_IodineWizard_Q3_IsForCTA_ImplicationWh.Source: For CTA, the iodine delivery rate and injection duration are the key variables.
T_IodineWizard_Q3_IsForCTA_ImplicationWh.Translation: Ved CTA er jodindgiftshastigheden og injektionsvarigheden de afgørende variabler.

T_IodineWizard_Q3_IsForCTA_Question.Source: Is this protocol used for CT angiography?

T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Guidan.Source:
Usually the answer to this is No, especially for very fast scans (< 10 seconds).

If you select Yes, the technologist can change the duration of the contrast phase from the current {0} seconds to what is needed for the scan.  This means the total iodine load may go up or down, based on the duration.
T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Guidan.Translation:
Svaret på dette er normalt Nej, især ved meget hurtige scanninger (<10 sekunder).

Hvis du vælger Ja, kan teknikeren ændre varigheden af kontrastfasen fra de aktuelle {0} sekunder til det, der er brug for til scanningen.  Dette betyder, at det samlede jodindhold kan gå op eller ned, baseret på varigheden.

T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Implic.Source: The technologist will not be able to change the injection duration.
The technologist can update the injection duration based on each patient's scan duration, and the protocol will recalculate.
T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Implic.Translation: Teknikeren kan opdatere injektionsvarigheden baseret på hver patients scanningsvarighed, og protokollen vil blive genberegnet.

T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Questi.Source: Do you need to be able to adjust the injection duration based on the scan duration?
T_IodineWizard_Q31_AdjustDuration_Questi.Translation: Skal injektionsvarigheden kunne justeres baseret på scanningsvarigheden?
